{"id":"decision-mini-001","type":"decision","fact":"mini is zero-dependency by design: package.json has no dependencies and no devDependencies. Tests run on node:test; coverage is native --experimental-test-coverage.","recommendation":"Do not add any runtime or dev dependency (no test framework, linter, mocking or coverage tool) without explicit approval. If a task seems to need one, stop and reconsider.","confidence":"high","provenance":[{"source":"human","reference":"README design principle #1 / CLAUDE.md","date":"2026-06-23"}],"tags":["architecture","zero-dependency","testing"],"affectedFiles":["package.json"],"affectedServices":[],"createdAt":"2026-06-23T00:00:00Z","updatedAt":"2026-06-23T00:00:00Z","usageCount":0,"helpfulCount":0,"outdatedReports":0}
{"id":"decision-mini-002","type":"decision","fact":"Plugins never touch the world directly: all HTTP/shell/prompt I/O goes through the injected ctx (ctx.http, ctx.shell, ctx.prompt). This is what makes 100% offline, fixture-replayed tests possible.","recommendation":"In a plugin, never require('https')/child_process or interpolate shell strings; use ctx.http.request and ctx.shell.capture/run with argument arrays.","confidence":"high","provenance":[{"source":"human","reference":"README design principle #3","date":"2026-06-23"}],"tags":["architecture","testing","seam"],"affectedFiles":["plugins/yt.js","plugins/cdk.js","lib/plugin-context.js"],"affectedServices":[],"createdAt":"2026-06-23T00:00:00Z","updatedAt":"2026-06-23T00:00:00Z","usageCount":0,"helpfulCount":0,"outdatedReports":0}
{"id":"decision-mini-003","type":"decision","fact":"Coverage thresholds in .coverage-thresholds.json are the honest current floor (not the 100% aspiration), set so the documented command actually passes. A gate that is always red is no gate.","recommendation":"Ratchet up to lock in gains as coverage improves; never lower thresholds to make a change pass. 100% stays the target.","confidence":"high","provenance":[{"source":"agent","reference":"self-assessment finding #3","date":"2026-06-23"}],"tags":["coverage","ci","process"],"affectedFiles":[".coverage-thresholds.json"],"affectedServices":[],"createdAt":"2026-06-23T00:00:00Z","updatedAt":"2026-06-23T00:00:00Z","usageCount":0,"helpfulCount":0,"outdatedReports":0}
